00:56:29,760 --> 00:56:31,980
[SPEAKER_01] prije nego ide u vojsku,

1586
00:56:32,679 --> 00:56:34,059
[SPEAKER_01] kad služe već vojni rok

1587
00:56:34,059 --> 00:56:34,880
[SPEAKER_01] u ti dva mjesta

1588
00:56:34,880 --> 00:56:36,420
[SPEAKER_01] po ovom ludom zakonu,

1589
00:56:36,420 --> 00:56:38,139
[SPEAKER_01] on nakon dva tjedna kaže

1590
00:56:38,139 --> 00:56:39,980
[SPEAKER_01] a ne bi ja pušku u ruke,

1591
00:56:39,980 --> 00:56:42,239
[SPEAKER_01] ja idem u ciljno služenje.

1592
00:56:42,239 --> 00:56:43,099
[SPEAKER_01] I on kaže

1593
00:56:43,099 --> 00:56:43,480
[SPEAKER_01] ok,

1594
00:56:43,480 --> 00:56:45,320
[SPEAKER_01] evo tebi prekidamo vojni rok,

1595
00:56:45,320 --> 00:56:45,719
[SPEAKER_01] ideš ti,

1596
00:56:45,719 --> 00:56:47,719
[SPEAKER_01] kad ga digne u priču,

1597
00:56:47,719 --> 00:56:48,559
[SPEAKER_01] on kaže

1598
00:56:48,559 --> 00:56:49,860
[SPEAKER_01] a ne bi ja si tu

1599
00:56:49,860 --> 00:56:50,780
[SPEAKER_01] deset dana s vama

1600
00:56:50,780 --> 00:56:51,320
[SPEAKER_01] po slunju,

1601
00:56:51,320 --> 00:56:51,780
[SPEAKER_01] naganju,

1602
00:56:51,780 --> 00:56:52,960
[SPEAKER_01] po blatu i kiši,

1603
00:56:52,960 --> 00:56:54,619
[SPEAKER_01] ja hoću od sad biti

1604
00:56:54,619 --> 00:56:55,420
[SPEAKER_01] ciljnjak,

1605
00:56:55,420 --> 00:56:56,500
[SPEAKER_01] hoću u ciljnu službu.

1606
00:56:56,500 --> 00:56:58,139
[SPEAKER_01] I tad ga ima pravostav.

1607
00:56:58,139 --> 00:57:00,039
[SPEAKER_01] Ali kad dođe rat,

1608
00:57:00,139 --> 00:57:02,219
[SPEAKER_01] draga moja gospođa,

1609
00:57:02,219 --> 00:57:03,980
[SPEAKER_01] takav pokvarenjak

1610
00:57:03,980 --> 00:57:05,559
[SPEAKER_01] ima pravo reći

1611
00:57:05,559 --> 00:57:06,719
[SPEAKER_01] ratnom zapovedniku

1612
00:57:06,719 --> 00:57:07,679
[SPEAKER_01] tamo kojega digne

1613
00:57:07,679 --> 00:57:09,179
[SPEAKER_01] rat je opća mobilizacija.

1614
00:57:09,179 --> 00:57:10,239
[SPEAKER_01] Ne, ne,

1615
00:57:10,239 --> 00:57:11,139
[SPEAKER_01] ma kaki,

1616
00:57:11,139 --> 00:57:12,300
[SPEAKER_01] ja odbijam

1617
00:57:12,300 --> 00:57:13,719
[SPEAKER_01] uzeti pušku u ruke,

1618
00:57:13,719 --> 00:57:14,380
[SPEAKER_01] ja neću.

1619
00:57:14,639 --> 00:57:16,840
[SPEAKER_01] pa koju državu ti braniš čovječe?

1620
00:57:16,840 --> 00:57:18,179
[SPEAKER_01] Pa dje ti živiš?

1621
00:57:18,179 --> 00:57:19,519
[SPEAKER_01] Pa šta ćemo mi,

1622
00:57:19,519 --> 00:57:20,639
[SPEAKER_01] sirotinska djeca,

1623
00:57:20,639 --> 00:57:22,079
[SPEAKER_01] tebe branit,

1624
00:57:22,079 --> 00:57:23,619
[SPEAKER_01] tebe pametnog,

1625
00:57:23,619 --> 00:57:24,679
[SPEAKER_01] koji ćeš

1626
00:57:24,679 --> 00:57:27,519
[SPEAKER_01] luftirat po kafićima guzu

1627
00:57:27,519 --> 00:57:29,000
[SPEAKER_01] ili otići izme Hrvatske,

1628
00:57:29,000 --> 00:57:29,800
[SPEAKER_01] a mi ćemo

1629
00:57:29,800 --> 00:57:30,659
[SPEAKER_01] tvoju slobodu,

1630
00:57:30,659 --> 00:57:31,900
[SPEAKER_01] tvoju imovinu,

1631
00:57:31,900 --> 00:57:32,940
[SPEAKER_01] tvoju braću,

1632
00:57:32,940 --> 00:57:33,440
[SPEAKER_01] sestre,

1633
00:57:33,440 --> 00:57:34,699
[SPEAKER_01] tebe branit.

1634
00:57:34,699 --> 00:57:36,320
[SPEAKER_01] Pa nema to u svijetu,

1635
00:57:36,320 --> 00:57:38,039
[SPEAKER_01] to samo lude države

1636
00:57:38,039 --> 00:57:38,900
[SPEAKER_01] mogu nešto tako.

1637
00:57:39,139 --> 00:57:41,559
[SPEAKER_01] to je toliko nakaradno,

1638
00:57:41,559 --> 00:57:42,679
[SPEAKER_01] to se treba mijenjati

1639
00:57:42,679 --> 00:57:44,559
[SPEAKER_01] i znači paralelno

1640
00:57:44,559 --> 00:57:46,760
[SPEAKER_01] uz zakon o uvođenju

1641
00:57:46,760 --> 00:57:47,400
[SPEAKER_01] vojnog roka,

1642
00:57:47,400 --> 00:57:48,659
[SPEAKER_01] ministar Anošić

1643
00:57:48,659 --> 00:57:50,840
[SPEAKER_01] mora dati prijedlog

1644
00:57:50,840 --> 00:57:51,679
[SPEAKER_01] izmena,

1645
00:57:51,679 --> 00:57:52,920
[SPEAKER_01] odnosno nadležni ministar,

1646
00:57:52,920 --> 00:57:54,719
[SPEAKER_01] to je za socijalnu skrb,

1647
00:57:54,719 --> 00:57:56,139
[SPEAKER_01] ta silna služba,

1648
00:57:56,139 --> 00:57:56,860
[SPEAKER_01] on je nadležan,

1649
00:57:56,860 --> 00:57:58,400
[SPEAKER_01] on mora dati prijedlog

1650
00:57:58,400 --> 00:58:00,119
[SPEAKER_01] izmene tog sudog zakona.

1651
00:58:00,119 --> 00:58:02,119
[SPEAKER_01] Vidim da na tom tragu

1652
00:58:02,119 --> 00:58:03,639
[SPEAKER_01] bi mogli imati razumijelanja

1653
00:58:03,639 --> 00:58:05,059
[SPEAKER_01] od gospodina Bavuka,

1654
00:58:05,059 --> 00:58:06,239
[SPEAKER_01] koji je jučer rekao

1655
00:58:06,239 --> 00:58:08,440
[SPEAKER_01] državno pravo na obranu

1656
00:58:08,440 --> 00:58:09,619
[SPEAKER_01] i je prioritetno.

1657
00:58:09,619 --> 00:58:11,699
[SPEAKER_01] A podredno tome,

1658
00:58:11,699 --> 00:58:14,059
[SPEAKER_01] subsidarno je pravo pojedinca

1659
00:58:14,059 --> 00:58:15,519
[SPEAKER_01] na priziv savesti.

1660
00:58:15,519 --> 00:58:16,900
[SPEAKER_01] Znači prije svega

1661
00:58:16,900 --> 00:58:17,539
[SPEAKER_00] izvoli brani državno.

1662
00:58:17,539 --> 00:58:18,739
[SPEAKER_01] Izvoli brani,

1663
00:58:18,739 --> 00:58:19,360
[SPEAKER_01] kad je rat,

1664
00:58:19,360 --> 00:58:20,159
[SPEAKER_01] rat je za sve,

1665
00:58:20,159 --> 00:58:21,099
[SPEAKER_01] kak je ona starica

1666
00:58:21,099 --> 00:58:22,039
[SPEAKER_01] uvako rekla.

1667
00:58:22,039 --> 00:58:22,619
[SPEAKER_01] Da, da.

1668
00:58:22,619 --> 00:58:24,440
[SPEAKER_00] Generale,

1669
00:58:24,440 --> 00:58:26,380
[SPEAKER_00] danas niste sad više

1670
00:58:26,380 --> 00:58:28,300
[SPEAKER_00] u novom sazivu sabora.

1671
00:58:28,300 --> 00:58:29,880
[SPEAKER_00] Kako danas gledate na sabor?

1672
00:58:29,880 --> 00:58:32,380
[SPEAKER_01] Pa oni funkcioniraju,

1673
00:58:32,380 --> 00:58:33,539
[SPEAKER_01] meni je žao što nema

1674
00:58:33,539 --> 00:58:34,739
[SPEAKER_01] toliko žestine.

1675
00:58:34,739 --> 00:58:36,260
[SPEAKER_01] Meni činim da je manje žestine

1676
00:58:36,260 --> 00:58:37,940
[SPEAKER_01] nego kad smo bili nas

1677
00:58:37,940 --> 00:58:39,519
[SPEAKER_01] nekolicina tamo.

1678
00:58:39,519 --> 00:58:41,500
[SPEAKER_00] Tko vam je onako top?

1679
00:58:41,500 --> 00:58:42,500
[SPEAKER_00] Tko vam je dobar?

1680
00:58:42,500 --> 00:58:43,139
[SPEAKER_00] Danas?

1681
00:58:43,139 --> 00:58:43,699
[SPEAKER_00] Da.

1682
00:58:43,699 --> 00:58:45,960
[SPEAKER_01] Pa standardno su mi Miletić,

1683
00:58:45,960 --> 00:58:46,780
[SPEAKER_01] Mostovc,

1684
00:58:46,780 --> 00:58:48,199
[SPEAKER_01] Miro Bulj,

1685
00:58:48,199 --> 00:58:49,659
[SPEAKER_01] Moj Pavliček,

1686
00:58:49,659 --> 00:58:51,900
[SPEAKER_01] profesor Jurčević.

1687
00:58:51,980 --> 00:58:53,380
[SPEAKER_01] sad da nekog ne zaboravim.

1688
00:58:53,380 --> 00:58:58,719
[SPEAKER_01] Oni su mi od te desne sfere.

1689
00:58:58,719 --> 00:59:00,880
[SPEAKER_01] Bili su mi nekak dobri

1690
00:59:00,880 --> 00:59:02,679
[SPEAKER_01] ovi s DP-a neki,

1691
00:59:02,679 --> 00:59:03,820
[SPEAKER_01] ali sad poslije izbora

1692
00:59:03,820 --> 00:59:05,760
[SPEAKER_01] kad sam vidio kako su se to prevrnuli,

1693
00:59:05,760 --> 00:59:07,159
[SPEAKER_01] opće ih ne pratim,

1694
00:59:07,159 --> 00:59:07,639
[SPEAKER_01] ne želim.

1695
00:59:07,639 --> 00:59:08,940
[SPEAKER_01] A tko vam diže živac?

1696
00:59:08,940 --> 00:59:10,039
[SPEAKER_01] Tko mi diže živac?

1697
00:59:10,039 --> 00:59:11,780
[SPEAKER_01] Pa ovi možemo si to,

1698
00:59:11,780 --> 00:59:12,940
[SPEAKER_01] to je brate Miline.

1699
00:59:12,940 --> 00:59:14,059
[SPEAKER_01] To je negledljivo,

1700
00:59:14,059 --> 00:59:14,860
[SPEAKER_01] nesvatljivo.

1701
00:59:16,739 --> 00:59:18,239
[SPEAKER_01] koliko je to odnarođeno,

1702
00:59:18,239 --> 00:59:20,280
[SPEAKER_01] koliko je to izvan Hrvatske,

1703
00:59:20,280 --> 00:59:21,800
[SPEAKER_01] koliko je to izvan obitelji,

1704
00:59:21,800 --> 00:59:24,280
[SPEAKER_01] koliko je to anacionalno šoroševski,

1705
00:59:24,280 --> 00:59:26,900
[SPEAKER_01] koliko je to baš ono užas,

1706
00:59:26,900 --> 00:59:27,559
[SPEAKER_01] užas.

1707
00:59:27,559 --> 00:59:29,760
[SPEAKER_01] Oni su mi najgori tu u tom smislu.

1708
00:59:29,760 --> 00:59:32,019
[SPEAKER_01] Šta vam najviše smeta danas u Hrvatskoj?

1709
00:59:32,019 --> 00:59:35,679
[SPEAKER_01] Pa najviše mi smeta lopovuk.

1710
00:59:35,679 --> 00:59:36,840
[SPEAKER_01] Na kraju.

1711
00:59:36,840 --> 00:59:41,139
[SPEAKER_01] Neodgovornost prema nacionalnim interesima,

1712
00:59:41,139 --> 00:59:42,639
[SPEAKER_01] znači bilo koje vrste,

1713
00:59:42,639 --> 00:59:46,159
[SPEAKER_01] ali osobito lopovuk koji se u Hrvatskoj isplati.

1714
00:59:46,679 --> 00:59:48,420
[SPEAKER_01] Nikad u svijetu je temno načelo

1715
00:59:48,420 --> 00:59:50,800
[SPEAKER_01] da se kriminal ne smije isplatiti.

1716
00:59:50,800 --> 00:59:52,739
[SPEAKER_01] Na tome djelujemo,

1717
00:59:52,739 --> 00:59:55,739
[SPEAKER_01] znači ta preventivna funkcija

1718
00:59:55,739 --> 00:59:57,019
[SPEAKER_01] od pradavnih vremena.

1719
00:59:57,019 --> 00:59:59,219
[SPEAKER_01] Međutim, u Hrvatskoj se nažalost

1720
00:59:59,219 --> 01:00:00,920
[SPEAKER_01] to isplati.

1721
01:00:00,920 --> 01:00:04,679
[SPEAKER_01] Iako imamo najsuvremenije zakonodavstvo

1722
01:00:04,679 --> 01:00:06,940
[SPEAKER_01] u tom pogledu za otkrivanje,

1723
01:00:06,940 --> 01:00:08,539
[SPEAKER_01] suzbijanje kazenih dijela,

1724
01:00:08,539 --> 01:00:09,659
[SPEAKER_01] kazenih zakona,

1725
01:00:09,659 --> 01:00:10,940
[SPEAKER_01] zakon o kazenu,

1726
01:00:10,940 --> 01:00:13,980
[SPEAKER_01] posebnih zakona o posebnim mjerama,

1727
01:00:13,980 --> 01:00:14,880
[SPEAKER_01] tajne pratnje,

1728
01:00:14,880 --> 01:00:16,139
[SPEAKER_01] prisluškivanja,

1729
01:00:16,619 --> 01:00:18,320
[SPEAKER_01] simulirani isporuka.

1730
01:00:18,320 --> 01:00:18,360
[SPEAKER_01] Sve ima.

1731
01:00:18,360 --> 01:00:21,800
[SPEAKER_01] Sve ko Amerikanci za pranje novca,

1732
01:00:21,800 --> 01:00:22,519
[SPEAKER_01] sve, sve, sve.

1733
01:00:22,519 --> 01:00:25,039
[SPEAKER_01] I banda neće to primjenjivati.

1734
01:00:25,039 --> 01:00:25,760
[SPEAKER_01] Zašto?

1735
01:00:25,760 --> 01:00:27,420
[SPEAKER_01] Ili su nesposobni,

1736
01:00:27,420 --> 01:00:28,760
[SPEAKER_01] ili su korumpirani,

1737
01:00:28,760 --> 01:00:30,260
[SPEAKER_01] ili su strašljivi.

1738
01:00:31,199 --> 01:00:32,139
[SPEAKER_01] nešto se događa.

1739
01:00:32,139 --> 01:00:33,079
[SPEAKER_01] Nešto katao.

1740
01:00:33,079 --> 01:00:36,980
[SPEAKER_01] Turudić bi tome morao i tekako posvetiti pažnje.

1741
01:00:36,980 --> 01:00:38,519
[SPEAKER_01] I s druge strane,

1742
01:00:38,519 --> 01:00:40,679
[SPEAKER_01] samo da vam tu kažem,

1743
01:00:40,679 --> 01:00:43,760
[SPEAKER_01] što, kad ste već rekli šta ima još jako pogađa.

1744
01:00:43,760 --> 01:00:46,039
[SPEAKER_01] Pogađa me ta zamjena stano nišla.

1745
01:00:46,039 --> 01:00:46,460
[SPEAKER_01] Gledajte,

1746
01:00:46,460 --> 01:00:49,940
[SPEAKER_01] ti ilegalni imigranti stvarno nas okupiraju,

1747
01:00:49,940 --> 01:00:51,800
[SPEAKER_01] ni luk jeli, ni mirisali,

1748
01:00:51,800 --> 01:00:52,920
[SPEAKER_01] bez zrna, baruta.

1749
01:00:52,920 --> 01:00:54,179
[SPEAKER_01] To se sad ne piše.

1750
01:00:54,179 --> 01:00:56,420
[SPEAKER_01] A oni kontinuirano dolaze tu na vaš kraj.

1751
01:00:56,420 --> 01:01:00,019
[SPEAKER_01] U grupi od troje, četvero, petero, šta ti ja znam.

1752
01:01:00,019 --> 01:01:03,599
[SPEAKER_01] Niti je ministar Božinović, niti je Andrej Plenković

1753
01:01:03,599 --> 01:01:06,460
[SPEAKER_01] išto učinkovito sve ove godine radio,

1754
01:01:06,460 --> 01:01:08,719
[SPEAKER_01] da na granici postavi taj štit.

1755
01:01:08,719 --> 01:01:14,820
[SPEAKER_01] A imali smo i imamo ustavno, međunarodno i zakonsko pravo.

1756
01:01:14,820 --> 01:01:19,000
[SPEAKER_01] Dao sam prijedlog zakona, potpisao ga sedamne zastupnika,

1757
01:01:19,000 --> 01:01:23,800
[SPEAKER_01] prijedlog izmjena zakona o međunarodnoj privremenoj zašti,

1758
01:01:24,039 --> 01:01:25,260
[SPEAKER_01] o azilu i tako dalje,

1759
01:01:25,260 --> 01:01:27,719
[SPEAKER_01] gdje je jedan šlanak treba izmijeniti.

1760
01:01:27,719 --> 01:01:32,619
[SPEAKER_01] I verno imao sam potporu i ljudi iz drugih branši,

1761
01:01:32,619 --> 01:01:34,380
[SPEAKER_01] ne samo desničara takozvani.

1762
01:01:34,380 --> 01:01:37,679
[SPEAKER_01] Međutim, nismo na dnevni red stavili, Androković,

1763
01:01:37,679 --> 01:01:43,960
[SPEAKER_01] gdje kažem, ne možete se hvaliti dnevnoj bazi

1764
01:01:43,960 --> 01:01:47,380
[SPEAKER_01] da ste uhitili dva, tri, pet krijumčara,

1765
01:01:47,380 --> 01:01:50,340
[SPEAKER_01] ljudi, tih ilegalni imigranata,

1766
01:01:50,340 --> 01:01:53,900
[SPEAKER_01] a ilegalni imigrante koje ste vozili u prikolici

1767
01:01:53,900 --> 01:01:58,800
[SPEAKER_01] u nekakvom bunkeru, potka, ne znam čemu,

1768
01:01:58,800 --> 01:02:04,659
[SPEAKER_01] nudite čajim, keksima i hoćete uzeti azil,

1769
01:02:04,659 --> 01:02:06,780
[SPEAKER_01] odite vi ste žrtve kaznog dijela.

1770
01:02:06,780 --> 01:02:09,440
[SPEAKER_01] To je suludo, to je protoustavno.

1771
01:02:09,440 --> 01:02:11,119
[SPEAKER_01] Tu Andrij Plenković, kad bi bio,

1772
01:02:11,119 --> 01:02:14,559
[SPEAKER_01] nas generale su po objektivnoj zapolim dvovornosti proganjali,

1773
01:02:14,559 --> 01:02:16,539
[SPEAKER_01] tu mu slijedi kaznina prijeva,

1774
01:02:16,539 --> 01:02:19,940
[SPEAKER_01] tu mu slijedi optužnica svima koji to toleriraju,

1775
01:02:19,940 --> 01:02:21,880
[SPEAKER_01] jer krši ustav,

1776
01:02:21,880 --> 01:02:23,460
[SPEAKER_01] da smo svi pred zakonom jednaki.

1777
01:02:23,880 --> 01:02:27,599
[SPEAKER_01] Znači, ako neko pročini kaznno dijelo koje je dvostranog oblika,

1778
01:02:27,599 --> 01:02:29,199
[SPEAKER_01] primanje, davanje mita,

1779
01:02:29,199 --> 01:02:33,760
[SPEAKER_01] ti procesuiraš i onoga koji prima, ali i onoga koji daje.

1780
01:02:33,760 --> 01:02:37,679
[SPEAKER_01] Ne može reći, ja ne bi ovaj primio da mu nije dao ili obrnuto.

1781
01:02:37,679 --> 01:02:42,260
[SPEAKER_01] Kod prostitucija, kod, ne znam, mnogih drugih kazninih dijela,

1782
01:02:42,260 --> 01:02:47,500
[SPEAKER_01] takve vrste, i sa skrivenim i otkrivenim žrtvama,

1783
01:02:47,500 --> 01:02:51,019
[SPEAKER_01] zakonodavac, kaznini zakon funkcionira na način

1784
01:02:51,019 --> 01:02:53,019
[SPEAKER_01] da se moraju svi kazniti.

1785
01:02:53,019 --> 01:02:56,420
[SPEAKER_01] Znači, ja sam tebe potaknuo, ti krijučar,

1786
01:02:56,420 --> 01:02:59,300
[SPEAKER_01] ja ste negdje našao, sa tvojim autom i rekli,

1787
01:02:59,300 --> 01:03:01,539
[SPEAKER_01] čuj krijučaru, evo ti tišu eura,

1788
01:03:01,539 --> 01:03:04,340
[SPEAKER_01] ne da mi se po tim šumama, potocima,

1789
01:03:04,340 --> 01:03:07,159
[SPEAKER_01] blatiti, mogu za zalječno minjskom polju,

1790
01:03:07,159 --> 01:03:11,039
[SPEAKER_01] evo ti tišu eura, evo mene i moji 5-6 prijatelja

1791
01:03:11,039 --> 01:03:14,039
[SPEAKER_01] provezi brzom trasom do Slovenije

1792
01:03:14,039 --> 01:03:17,099
[SPEAKER_01] i tamo iz Hrca i sve okej.

1793
01:03:17,099 --> 01:03:19,619
[SPEAKER_01] A ovi moji prijatelji neki idu šumama i gorama,

1794
01:03:19,619 --> 01:03:20,579
[SPEAKER_01] pa dok ne stigno.

1795
01:03:20,579 --> 01:03:23,860
[SPEAKER_01] I krijučar pristane da trpa lovu džep

1796
01:03:23,860 --> 01:03:27,639
[SPEAKER_01] u kombi i teraj, dok negdje ne slone.

1797
01:03:27,639 --> 01:03:31,420
[SPEAKER_01] I sad kad ga policija, znači, ovo je koji ga potaknu,

1798
01:03:31,420 --> 01:03:35,739
[SPEAKER_01] to je poticatelj kaznog dijela u rangu izvršiteljstva.

1799
01:03:35,739 --> 01:03:40,340
[SPEAKER_01] Kako izvrštelj odgovara, tako i poticatelj odgovara.

1800
01:03:40,340 --> 01:03:43,139
[SPEAKER_01] Kaznog pravda. Nema, nema iznimke.

1801
01:03:43,139 --> 01:03:46,599
[SPEAKER_01] Međutim, naš Andrej Plejković, naš Božinović,

1802
01:03:46,599 --> 01:03:49,539
[SPEAKER_01] naš glavni ravnatelj policije,

1803
01:03:49,539 --> 01:03:52,880
[SPEAKER_01] naša policija, zahvaljujući toj naredbi političkoj,

1804
01:03:52,880 --> 01:03:55,179
[SPEAKER_01] njima gledaju kroz prste.

1805
01:03:55,920 --> 01:04:00,400
[SPEAKER_01] Zašto gledati? Oni su na taj način legalno prošvercali u Orvatsku

1806
01:04:00,400 --> 01:04:03,860
[SPEAKER_01] najmanje 25.000 takvih ilegalni imigranata

1807
01:04:03,860 --> 01:04:05,679
[SPEAKER_01] u ovi zadnjih 5-6 godina.

1808
01:04:05,679 --> 01:04:10,880
[SPEAKER_01] Znači, kao krijučare su procesuirali njih tisuću,

1809
01:04:10,880 --> 01:04:14,280
[SPEAKER_01] a ove kao žrtve, oni su žrtve, pazite molite,

1810
01:04:14,280 --> 01:04:16,860
[SPEAKER_01] on je dao 1000 eura i on je žrtva.

1811
01:04:16,860 --> 01:04:19,019
[SPEAKER_01] Kakva su ti žrtva čoveče?

1812
01:04:19,179 --> 01:04:21,239
[SPEAKER_00] Ali vraćaju ih avionima.

1813
01:04:21,239 --> 01:04:23,119
[SPEAKER_00] E, to je druga priča.

1814
01:04:23,119 --> 01:04:24,880
[SPEAKER_01] Ali sam da vam ovo kažem.

1815
01:04:24,880 --> 01:04:28,340
[SPEAKER_01] Kad sam to ispričao, tu svoju priču, sad, vama,

1816
01:04:28,340 --> 01:04:30,900
[SPEAKER_01] da se krši ustavi, krši kazni zakon,

1817
01:04:30,900 --> 01:04:38,280
[SPEAKER_01] gospodino Emiliju, kandidatu Karabriću,

1818
01:04:38,280 --> 01:04:40,420
[SPEAKER_01] kandidatu za glavnu državnog odjednika,

1819
01:04:40,420 --> 01:04:42,940
[SPEAKER_01] kad je Turić zabran, pa smo imali javno predstavljeno,

1820
01:04:42,940 --> 01:04:45,059
[SPEAKER_01] kad sam to rekao, šta on o tome misli,

1821
01:04:45,980 --> 01:04:50,179
[SPEAKER_01] da li po njemu bi trebali odgovarati ti takozvane žrtve,

1822
01:04:50,179 --> 01:04:52,260
[SPEAKER_01] ilegalne, on je rekao, gospode, sad ću,

1823
01:04:52,260 --> 01:04:54,019
[SPEAKER_01] a on je sad zamenili glavnog državnog,

1824
01:04:54,019 --> 01:04:57,400
[SPEAKER_01] kad bi to tako bilo kako vi meni objašnjavate,

1825
01:04:57,400 --> 01:04:59,059
[SPEAKER_01] to je čisto kaznino dijelo.

1826
01:04:59,059 --> 01:05:03,420
[SPEAKER_01] Prema tome, Božinoviću, Andrej Plenkoviću,

1827
01:05:03,420 --> 01:05:04,679
[SPEAKER_01] izvršavajte.

1828
01:05:04,679 --> 01:05:07,940
[SPEAKER_01] Niste dodili u Sabor predlog zakona

1829
01:05:07,940 --> 01:05:08,840
[SPEAKER_01] koji bi rekao,

1830
01:05:08,840 --> 01:05:12,320
[SPEAKER_01] oni koji se voze u kamperima,

1831
01:05:12,320 --> 01:05:13,659
[SPEAKER_01] autobusima, kamionima,

1832
01:05:13,800 --> 01:05:16,780
[SPEAKER_01] koji kljumčari Švercaju su žrtve kaznog dijela.

1833
01:05:16,780 --> 01:05:21,059
[SPEAKER_01] Tek tad oni ne bi mogli biti kaznino procesuirani.

1834
01:05:21,059 --> 01:05:23,960
[SPEAKER_01] A onda mi jednom prilikom gospodin Božinović rekao,

1835
01:05:23,960 --> 01:05:26,340
[SPEAKER_01] kad bi mi sve te u zatvor,

1836
01:05:26,340 --> 01:05:28,059
[SPEAKER_01] pa koliko bi zatvora morali imat?

1837
01:05:28,059 --> 01:05:29,800
[SPEAKER_01] Pa napravi ko Talijan,

1838
01:05:29,800 --> 01:05:30,739
[SPEAKER_01] napravi zatvor,

1839
01:05:30,739 --> 01:05:34,199
[SPEAKER_01] Talijan Meloni napravila u Albani zatvor za takve,

1840
01:05:34,199 --> 01:05:37,559
[SPEAKER_01] ili nekakvo prihvatilište.

1841
01:05:37,880 --> 01:05:39,460
[SPEAKER_01] Ali na primjer Poljska.

1842
01:05:39,460 --> 01:05:41,940
[SPEAKER_01] Poljska isto, pa šta bi Poljska napravila?

1843
01:05:41,940 --> 01:05:43,860
[SPEAKER_01] Pa napravi kako očeš,

1844
01:05:43,860 --> 01:05:45,300
[SPEAKER_01] ali ne možeš takve ljude

1845
01:05:45,300 --> 01:05:47,840
[SPEAKER_01] koji su sloni kriminalu držati u Hrvatskoj

1846
01:05:47,840 --> 01:05:49,460
[SPEAKER_01] i pustiti ih nakon toga,

1847
01:05:49,460 --> 01:05:52,340
[SPEAKER_01] on bude tamo dan, dva i šeće po Hrvatskoj.

1848
01:05:52,340 --> 01:05:53,300
[SPEAKER_01] Ove što kažete,

1849
01:05:53,300 --> 01:05:54,460
[SPEAKER_01] Tajnim letovima iz Svicarske.

1850
01:05:54,460 --> 01:05:55,679
[SPEAKER_01] Da, dajte mi to komentirati.

1851
01:05:55,679 --> 01:05:57,739
[SPEAKER_01] Ništa, to su znači najgori ološ,

1852
01:05:57,739 --> 01:05:59,400
[SPEAKER_01] kojima ne može

1853
01:05:59,400 --> 01:06:02,320
[SPEAKER_01] pravni sustav Njemačke,

1854
01:06:02,320 --> 01:06:03,739
[SPEAKER_01] Švicarske, Francuske,

1855
01:06:03,739 --> 01:06:05,639
[SPEAKER_01] doći na kraj Danske,

1856
01:06:05,639 --> 01:06:07,480
[SPEAKER_01] Gore, Norvečke, Švedske,

1857
01:06:07,480 --> 01:06:09,000
[SPEAKER_01] tužilo ga,

1858
01:06:09,000 --> 01:06:10,699
[SPEAKER_01] sjedio u zatvoru,

1859
01:06:10,699 --> 01:06:11,880
[SPEAKER_01] ponavlja kazan dijela,

1860
01:06:11,880 --> 01:06:13,159
[SPEAKER_01] silo je, krade,

1861
01:06:13,159 --> 01:06:14,099
[SPEAKER_01] nože mu vada

1862
01:06:14,099 --> 01:06:16,079
[SPEAKER_01] i oni ne mogu više šta s njim

1863
01:06:16,079 --> 01:06:16,980
[SPEAKER_01] i onda kažu,

1864
01:06:16,980 --> 01:06:18,780
[SPEAKER_01] slučaj, neće zdobiti azilu

1865
01:06:18,780 --> 01:06:19,840
[SPEAKER_01] u Švedskoj,

1866
01:06:19,840 --> 01:06:22,559
[SPEAKER_01] aj ti tamo rješavaj svoje probleme

1867
01:06:22,559 --> 01:06:23,099
[SPEAKER_01] s Hrvatskom,

1868
01:06:23,099 --> 01:06:24,460
[SPEAKER_01] tu si prvi put ušao.

1869
01:06:24,460 --> 01:06:25,719
[SPEAKER_01] Jel vi znate...

1870
01:06:25,719 --> 01:06:27,039
[SPEAKER_01] Pa koje sto ludosti?

1871
01:06:27,340 --> 01:06:29,420
[SPEAKER_01] i sad ovaj Božinović kaže

1872
01:06:29,420 --> 01:06:31,179
[SPEAKER_01] dobro, mi primamo

1873
01:06:31,179 --> 01:06:32,699
[SPEAKER_01] i znaš šta napravi?

1874
01:06:32,699 --> 01:06:34,360
[SPEAKER_01] Jedan dan tamo uzme

1875
01:06:34,360 --> 01:06:35,960
[SPEAKER_01] jes ti taj, jesam, jesam

1876
01:06:35,960 --> 01:06:38,099
[SPEAKER_01] i šta, sat u dva sata noću,

1877
01:06:38,099 --> 01:06:39,139
[SPEAKER_01] a ništa,

1878
01:06:39,139 --> 01:06:40,500
[SPEAKER_01] ajdi, snađi se negdje,

1879
01:06:40,500 --> 01:06:41,480
[SPEAKER_01] idi, snađi se pješće.

1880
01:06:41,480 --> 01:06:42,599
[SPEAKER_01] Pa to me zanima, znate?

1881
01:06:42,599 --> 01:06:44,679
[SPEAKER_01] I oni su opet laovi

1882
01:06:44,679 --> 01:06:45,780
[SPEAKER_01] ili hijene

1883
01:06:45,780 --> 01:06:47,519
[SPEAKER_01] među Srnama,

1884
01:06:47,519 --> 01:06:48,579
[SPEAKER_01] među Hrvatsama,

1885
01:06:48,579 --> 01:06:49,300
[SPEAKER_01] Hrvatima,

1886
01:06:49,300 --> 01:06:50,519
[SPEAKER_01] šetaju među nam.

1887
01:06:50,519 --> 01:06:52,019
[SPEAKER_01] Pa to je odgovornost

1888
01:06:52,019 --> 01:06:53,780
[SPEAKER_01] tog Plenkovića i Božinovića.

1889
01:06:53,780 --> 01:06:55,500
[SPEAKER_01] Ko će vas opratno toga?

1890
01:06:55,900 --> 01:06:57,739
[SPEAKER_01] Kad vam dođe Sačić na vlast,

1891
01:06:57,739 --> 01:06:58,940
[SPEAKER_01] odgovarat ćete svi.

1892
01:06:58,940 --> 01:07:00,719
[SPEAKER_01] O tome ćete odgovarati.

1893
01:07:00,719 --> 01:07:02,139
[SPEAKER_01] To nije osveta.

1894
01:07:02,139 --> 01:07:04,719
[SPEAKER_01] To je vaša povijesna odgovornost.

1895
01:07:04,719 --> 01:07:06,360
[SPEAKER_01] Kao što ste nas, generale,

1896
01:07:06,360 --> 01:07:07,400
[SPEAKER_01] za ništa proganjali,

1897
01:07:07,400 --> 01:07:08,960
[SPEAKER_01] za objektivnu odgovornost

1898
01:07:08,960 --> 01:07:10,119
[SPEAKER_01] i vi ćete se suočiti

1899
01:07:10,119 --> 01:07:11,300
[SPEAKER_01] sa objektivnom odgovornost.

1900
01:07:11,300 --> 01:07:13,639
[SPEAKER_01] Ali narod Sačića neće izabrat.

1901
01:07:13,639 --> 01:07:15,639
[SPEAKER_01] I to ti je poanta priče.

1902
01:07:15,639 --> 01:07:19,280
[SPEAKER_00] Da, ali zna narod

1903
01:07:19,280 --> 01:07:21,000
[SPEAKER_00] pisat komentare po fejtu.

1904
01:07:21,000 --> 01:07:21,559
[SPEAKER_00] To zna.

1905
01:07:21,559 --> 01:07:22,159
[SPEAKER_00] Kako ništa ne valja.

1906
01:07:22,159 --> 01:07:23,099
[SPEAKER_00] Ali dajte molim vas,

1907
01:07:23,099 --> 01:07:23,699
[SPEAKER_00] jel vi znate

1908
01:07:23,699 --> 01:07:25,079
[SPEAKER_00] što se onda s tim ljudima

1909
01:07:25,079 --> 01:07:26,760
[SPEAKER_00] koji dolaze avionima

1910
01:07:26,760 --> 01:07:28,320
[SPEAKER_00] natrag događa u Hrvatskoj?

1911
01:07:28,320 --> 01:07:28,719
[SPEAKER_01] Ništa.

1912
01:07:28,719 --> 01:07:29,880
[SPEAKER_01] Šetaju među nama

1913
01:07:29,880 --> 01:07:31,000
[SPEAKER_01] i on vam onda

1914
01:07:31,000 --> 01:07:32,360
[SPEAKER_01] kaže ovaj da ga pusti

1915
01:07:32,360 --> 01:07:33,579
[SPEAKER_01] i oni su tu među nama.

1916
01:07:34,119 --> 01:07:35,639
[SPEAKER_01] I sad kad mu padne na pamet

1917
01:07:35,639 --> 01:07:38,380
[SPEAKER_01] vidi on tu moj život,

1918
01:07:38,380 --> 01:07:39,179
[SPEAKER_01] moj je loš ovdje.

1919
01:07:39,179 --> 01:07:40,960
[SPEAKER_01] Ne znam koliko mu daju evora

1920
01:07:40,960 --> 01:07:41,380
[SPEAKER_01] i tako da.

1921
01:07:41,380 --> 01:07:42,320
[SPEAKER_01] Da, i njima je loš.

1922
01:07:42,320 --> 01:07:43,219
[SPEAKER_01] Pa loš je njima.

1923
01:07:43,219 --> 01:07:44,940
[SPEAKER_01] Čak vi se da su neki u Bosnu,

1924
01:07:44,940 --> 01:07:45,460
[SPEAKER_01] su povijeli,

1925
01:07:45,460 --> 01:07:46,780
[SPEAKER_01] ne možemo Hrvatskoj izdržati.

1926
01:07:46,780 --> 01:07:49,519
[SPEAKER_01] E onda se opet oni sami

1927
01:07:49,519 --> 01:07:50,679
[SPEAKER_01] na svoju ruku odluče

1928
01:07:50,679 --> 01:07:51,739
[SPEAKER_01] otišu u Njemačku.

1929
01:07:51,739 --> 01:07:53,440
[SPEAKER_01] Opet, ono, to napravite.

1930
01:07:53,440 --> 01:07:54,000
[SPEAKER_01] Da.

1931
01:07:54,000 --> 01:07:56,400
[SPEAKER_00] I šta onda reći za takvu državu?

1932
01:07:56,400 --> 01:07:58,179
[SPEAKER_00] Šta onda reći za takvu državu?

1933
01:07:58,179 --> 01:08:00,360
[SPEAKER_01] Ne radite vlado svoj posao.

1934
01:08:00,480 --> 01:08:01,300
[SPEAKER_01] Neodvorni ste.

1935
01:08:01,300 --> 01:08:03,699
[SPEAKER_01] DP tamo je ušao

1936
01:08:03,699 --> 01:08:04,860
[SPEAKER_01] kao da popravi stanje.

1937
01:08:04,860 --> 01:08:06,519
[SPEAKER_01] Pa DP dežurat morate

1938
01:08:06,519 --> 01:08:07,980
[SPEAKER_01] kontinirano pred vladom,

1939
01:08:07,980 --> 01:08:09,179
[SPEAKER_01] pred Plenkovićem.

1940
01:08:09,179 --> 01:08:10,880
[SPEAKER_01] Popis problema je reć.

1941
01:08:10,880 --> 01:08:12,179
[SPEAKER_01] Plenković urečava je to.

1942
01:08:12,179 --> 01:08:13,360
[SPEAKER_01] To, to.

1943
01:08:13,360 --> 01:08:15,559
[SPEAKER_01] Sutra za pet dana se vidimo

1944
01:08:15,559 --> 01:08:16,859
[SPEAKER_01] nekog iz DP-a

1945
01:08:16,859 --> 01:08:17,960
[SPEAKER_01] kao da su ona prava.

1946
01:08:17,960 --> 01:08:21,600
[SPEAKER_01] Oni su kao nešto oporba u vladi.

1947
01:08:21,600 --> 01:08:22,899
[SPEAKER_01] A onda bih rekao

1948
01:08:22,899 --> 01:08:24,340
[SPEAKER_01] za pet dana dolazimo

1949
01:08:24,340 --> 01:08:25,079
[SPEAKER_01] šta s Plenković?

1950
01:08:25,079 --> 01:08:27,020
[SPEAKER_01] Drže ključeve vladi.

1951
01:08:27,020 --> 01:08:28,060
[SPEAKER_01] E kao tako.

1952
01:08:28,060 --> 01:08:28,340
[SPEAKER_01] Da.

1953
01:08:28,340 --> 01:08:29,920
[SPEAKER_01] Pa da se oni tako ponašaju

1954
01:08:29,920 --> 01:08:30,800
[SPEAKER_01] i tako bi radili.

1955
01:08:30,800 --> 01:08:32,300
[SPEAKER_01] Međutim, ništa.

1956
01:08:32,300 --> 01:08:33,260
[SPEAKER_01] Dvuk pojom Agare

1957
01:08:33,260 --> 01:08:33,939
[SPEAKER_01] nima fino,

1958
01:08:33,939 --> 01:08:34,699
[SPEAKER_01] nima dobro,

1959
01:08:34,699 --> 01:08:35,880
[SPEAKER_01] dobro zapuso.

1960
01:08:35,880 --> 01:08:37,220
[SPEAKER_01] Vratio se iz pritvora

1961
01:08:37,220 --> 01:08:38,279
[SPEAKER_01] u sabor

1962
01:08:38,279 --> 01:08:39,039
[SPEAKER_01] i opet

1963
01:08:39,039 --> 01:08:40,399
[SPEAKER_01] nakon svih ti silni

1964
01:08:40,399 --> 01:08:41,260
[SPEAKER_01] neće on

1965
01:08:41,260 --> 01:08:42,619
[SPEAKER_01] podržavati vladu.

1966
01:08:42,619 --> 01:08:44,039
[SPEAKER_01] Kriminal se dubuka država.

1967
01:08:44,039 --> 01:08:45,020
[SPEAKER_01] Eto, diže ručice

1968
01:08:45,020 --> 01:08:45,520
[SPEAKER_01] oba dvije

1969
01:08:45,520 --> 01:08:46,800
[SPEAKER_01] povremeno i noge

1970
01:08:46,800 --> 01:08:47,340
[SPEAKER_01] i to je to.

1971
01:08:48,380 --> 01:08:49,640
[SPEAKER_00] da vas pitam za kraj.

1972
01:08:49,640 --> 01:08:51,800
[SPEAKER_00] Ožujak, odnosno kraj ožujka

1973
01:08:51,800 --> 01:08:53,619
[SPEAKER_00] obično je u kolektivnom sjećanju

1974
01:08:53,619 --> 01:08:56,300
[SPEAKER_00] našeg naroda

1975
01:08:56,300 --> 01:08:58,579
[SPEAKER_00] vezan za 31. ožujka

1976
01:08:58,579 --> 01:09:01,140
[SPEAKER_00] 91. odnosno za krvavi uskrs

1977
01:09:01,140 --> 01:09:01,800
[SPEAKER_00] na Plitvicama.

1978
01:09:01,800 --> 01:09:03,100
[SPEAKER_00] Bili ste tamo.

1979
01:09:03,159 --> 01:09:06,159
[SPEAKER_00] Sad, to su neki trenuci

1980
01:09:06,159 --> 01:09:07,800
[SPEAKER_00] koji su, to je početak

1981
01:09:07,800 --> 01:09:10,079
[SPEAKER_00] svega, promijenili mnoge.

1982
01:09:10,079 --> 01:09:11,220
[SPEAKER_00] Kako biste vi rekli,

1983
01:09:11,220 --> 01:09:12,520
[SPEAKER_00] od mnogih su možda

1984
