01:14:50,699 --> 01:14:52,939
[SPEAKER_01] Oni u tebe vide povjerenje,

2197
01:14:52,939 --> 01:14:54,739
[SPEAKER_01] ti se njima posvjeti

2198
01:14:54,739 --> 01:14:56,300
[SPEAKER_01] i tvoja ti je zadača

2199
01:14:56,300 --> 01:14:57,640
[SPEAKER_01] da vodiš računa

2200
01:14:57,640 --> 01:14:58,800
[SPEAKER_01] o njihovim životima,

2201
01:14:58,800 --> 01:15:00,640
[SPEAKER_01] a vrati se kući.

2202
01:15:00,640 --> 01:15:01,039
[SPEAKER_01] Eto.

2203
01:15:01,039 --> 01:15:03,439
[SPEAKER_00] I sad sam vas na kraju

2204
01:15:03,439 --> 01:15:04,079
