2205
01:15:04,079 --> 01:15:05,039
[SPEAKER_00] Pa niste.

2206
01:15:05,039 --> 01:15:07,779
[SPEAKER_01] To je moj emotivni ovako,

2207
01:15:07,779 --> 01:15:10,659
