2208
01:15:10,659 --> 01:15:15,260
[SPEAKER_01] i moja zapravo od Boga dana kvaliteta

2209
01:15:15,260 --> 01:15:17,560
[SPEAKER_01] da mogu na pravdu,

2210
01:15:17,560 --> 01:15:19,479
[SPEAKER_01] za pravdu i poginut,

2211
01:15:19,479 --> 01:15:22,699
[SPEAKER_01] a za nepravdu isto ne štedit se.

2212
01:15:22,699 --> 01:15:23,600
[SPEAKER_00] Borit se.

2213
01:15:23,600 --> 01:15:24,220
[SPEAKER_01] Tako je.

2214
01:15:24,220 --> 01:15:25,420
[SPEAKER_01] Protiv nije.

2215
01:15:25,739 --> 01:15:26,939
[SPEAKER_00] Gospodine Sačiću,

2216
01:15:26,939 --> 01:15:28,079
[SPEAKER_00] hvala vam na vremenu

2217
01:15:28,079 --> 01:15:29,579
[SPEAKER_00] koje ste ozlojili za nas.

2218
01:15:29,579 --> 01:15:31,140
[SPEAKER_00] Svako dobro vam želim.

2219
01:15:31,140 --> 01:15:32,720
[SPEAKER_00] Šteta što vas nema u Sabaru.

2220
01:15:32,720 --> 01:15:35,859
[SPEAKER_00] Sad će se netko i s tim porugati,

2221
01:15:35,859 --> 01:15:37,359
[SPEAKER_00] odnosno izrugivati,

2222
01:15:37,359 --> 01:15:39,520
[SPEAKER_00] ali ja ću reći baš je šteta što vas nema u Sabaru.

2223
01:15:39,520 --> 01:15:40,760
[SPEAKER_01] Pa mnogi su mi to rekli.

2224
01:15:40,760 --> 01:15:41,539
[SPEAKER_01] A šta ćete ti?

2225
01:15:41,539 --> 01:15:44,979
[SPEAKER_01] Bio sam neočekivano iznenađen.

2226
01:15:44,979 --> 01:15:47,659
[SPEAKER_01] Mislio sam u tom mom kraju u Zagorju.

2227
01:15:47,659 --> 01:15:51,060
[SPEAKER_01] Ako svog hrvatskog sina Sačića ne poznajete,

2228
01:15:51,060 --> 01:15:54,199
[SPEAKER_01] pet posto da mu dajete nakon svega da uže,

2229
01:15:54,279 --> 01:15:56,300
[SPEAKER_01] pa niste ni zavrijedili onda Sačića.

2230
01:15:56,300 --> 01:15:57,619
[SPEAKER_01] Niste ni zavrijedili.

2231
01:15:57,619 --> 01:15:59,600
[SPEAKER_00] Hvala vam najljepši.

2232
01:15:59,600 --> 01:16:00,039
[SPEAKER_00] Molim.

2233
01:16:00,039 --> 01:16:01,539
[SPEAKER_00] Svako dobro vam želim.

2234
01:16:01,539 --> 01:16:04,239
[SPEAKER_00] Dragi naši gledatelji podcasta Mrežnica,

2235
