2238
01:16:14,140 --> 01:16:15,220
[SPEAKER_00] Još jedan put vama hvala.

2239
01:16:15,220 --> 01:16:17,479
[SPEAKER_00] A vama, dragi naši, hvala što nas gledate.

2240
01:16:17,479 --> 01:16:18,760
[SPEAKER_00] Svako dobro vam želim.

